acsNew %>%
  group_by(FamilyType) %>%
  summarise(ile = n()) %>%
  arrange(desc(ile)) %>%
  mutate(prop = ile / sum(ile) * 100) %>%
  mutate(ypos = cumsum(prop) - 0.5*prop ) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = "", y = prop, fill = FamilyType)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 1, color = "white") +
  coord_polar("y", start = 0) +
  theme_void() + 
  theme(legend.position = "none") +
  geom_text(aes(y = ypos, label = FamilyType), color = "white", size = 4) +
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Set2") +
  labs(title = "Wykres koÅ‚owy typÃ³w rodzin w NY",
       caption = "Opracowanie wÅ‚asne na podstawie dany J.Landera",
       subtitle = "Dane z roku 2002") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, color = "peru"),
        plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust = 1, color = "yellowgreen"))

acsNew %>%
  group_by(FamilyType) %>%
  summarise(count = n()) %>%
  arrange(desc(count)) %>%
  mutate(fraction = count / sum(count),
         ymax = cumsum(fraction),
         ymin = c(0, head(ymax, n = -1))) %>%
  ggplot(aes(ymax = ymax, ymin = ymin, xmax = 4, xmin = 3, fill = FamilyType)) +
  geom_rect() +
  coord_polar(theta = "y") + 
  xlim(c(2, 4)) +
  theme_void()
